                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300527-216-off1142 t18300527-216-cd1143"></join>, 2 3/4 lbs. of soap, value 18d., and 3 lbs. weight of flour, value 6d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300527-216-victim1775" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Wilson
                        <interp inst="t18300527-216-victim1775" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
